description: The index is designed by Bloomberg Index Services Limited to consist of U.S. and non-U.S. equity securities of companies that have been classified by the index provider as providing exposure to the “Future of Finance”, as identified by the intersection of finance, technology and digital assets. Under normal circumstances, at least 80% of the fund’s net assets, plus borrowings for investment purposes, will be invested in the component securities of the index. It is non-diversified.
name: Grayscale Future of Finance ETF
